<p>Hello,</p>

<p>
  We are contacting you on behalf of <%= @shop.user.name %>, the owner of <%= @shop.name %> because they need your help with setting up ShopStream tracking for their shop.
</p>

<p>To start tracking, simply add this line to every page of your shop.</p>

<code>
  <p><pre>&lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot; src=&quot;<%= @shop.tracker_script_url %>&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</pre></p>
</code>

<p>And this JS code to every purchase-successful page.</p>

<code>
  <p><pre>
var _shopstream = _shopstream || [];

_shopstream.push(['addOrder',
  "Order name", // order name, required
  20.02, // order total, required
  "email@customer.com", // customer email, required
  "first", // customer first name, optional
  "last" // customer last name, optional
]);
_shopstream.push(['addItem',
  "SOME123SKU", // item SKU, required
  "Title", // item name, required
  10.01, // item price, required
  2 // item quantity, required
]);
_shopstream.push(['trackOrder']);
  </pre></p>
</code>

<p>Have a good day!</p>
